BuilderFactory builderFactory = new DefaultUriBuilderFactory();\n        builderFactory.setEncodingMode(DefaultUriBuilderFactory.EncodingMode.VALUES_ONLY);\n        RestTemplate restTemplate = new RestTemplate();\n        restTemplate.setUriTemplateHandler(builderFactory);\n\nThen there will be no need for spring-boot", "url": "https://github.com/odpi/egeria/pull/2884#discussion_r405100560", "createdAt": "2020-04-07T20:44:03Z", "author": {"login": "immmus"}, "path": "open-metadata-implementation/adapters/open-connectors/rest-client-connectors/spring-rest-client-connector/pom.xml", "diffHunk": "@@ -52,6 +52,11 @@\n             <groupId>org.codehaus.plexus</groupId>\n             <artifactId>plexus-utils</artifactId>\n         </dependency>\n+\n+        <dependency>", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQwNDk1Njg0NQ=="}, "originalCommit": {"oid": "8a164534d8f2de9d3978a32b35dde84adbe2b5e3"}, "originalPosition": 5}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQwNTMyODgyOA==", "bodyText": "Many thanks @planetf1 and @immus.\nI've made the above change and removed the dependency on spring-boot. That is much nicer :-)", "url": "https://github.com/odpi/egeria/pull/2884#discussion_r405328828", "createdAt": "2020-04-08T07:56:33Z", "author": {"login": "grahamwallis"}, "path": "open-metadata-implementation/adapters/open-connectors/rest-client-connectors/spring-rest-client-connector/pom.xml", "diffHunk": "@@ -52,6 +52,11 @@\n             <groupId>org.codehaus.plexus</groupId>\n             <artifactId>plexus-utils</artifactId>\n         </dependency>\n+\n+        <dependency>", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQwNDk1Njg0NQ=="}, "originalCommit": {"oid": "8a164534d8f2de9d3978a32b35dde84adbe2b5e3"}, "originalPosition": 5}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQwNTMzMjc1OQ==", "bodyText": "We are of course using restTemplate which is deprecated - https://docs.spring.io/spring-framewor